# D1 database files (glob, not the dir itself, so newer files can be negated back in)
cf-worker/migrations/*
# Post-cutover Postgres migrations are code (DDL + runbook) and must ship in the repo;
# only the legacy D1-era contents of migrations/ stay local. Negate new ones explicitly.
# Track ALL numbered migrations by default (a per-file list silently dropped 006
# and blinded the CI migration guard, 2026-07-07); only the legacy D1-era 001
# stays local.
!cf-worker/migrations/0*.sql
cf-worker/migrations/001_*.sql

# Local-only archive of stale docs (preserved on disk, not tracked)
